ident or intentional<br />\n&bull;Van struck up to ten people on Yonge St. near Finch Ave, Toronto at 1.30pm<br />\n&bull;Driver fled the scene but was stopped and arrested just a few blocks away<br />\n</ul> <br />\n<img src=\"http://i.dailymail.co.uk/i/newpix/2018/04/23/21/4B7866E900000578-5648591-image-a-11_1524516746807.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.dailymail.co.uk%2Fi%2Fnewpix%2F2018%2F04%2F23%2F21%2F4B7866E900000578-5648591-image-a-11_1524516746807.jpg&h=75a4e366&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://i.dailymail.co.uk/i/newpix/2018/04/23/19/4B78008F00000578-5648591-image-m-4_1524507681074.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.dailymail.co.uk%2Fi%2Fnewpix%2F2018%2F04%2F23%2F19%2F4B78008F00000578-5648591-image-m-4_1524507681074.jpg&h=a0f7521d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n A white van has mowed down at least eight pedestrians in Canada , police say. Pictured, first responders treat some of the injured at the scene<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://i.dailymail.co.uk/i/newpix/2018/04/23/21/4B784A1500000578-5648591-image-a-8_1524515366780.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.dailymail.co.uk%2Fi%2Fnewpix%2F2018%2F04%2F23%2F21%2F4B784A1500000578-5648591-image-a-8_1524515366780.jpg&h=ba9b85ba&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n A police officer stands next to a victim of an incident where a van struck multiple people at a major intersection in Toronto's northern suburbs <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://i.dailymail.co.uk/i/newpix/2018/04/23/21/4B78638500000578-5648591-image-a-12_1524516777721.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.dailymail.co.uk%2Fi%2Fnewpix%2F2018%2F04%2F23%2F21%2F4B78638500000578-5648591-image-a-12_1524516777721.jpg&h=8f62623d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n A body lies covered on the sidewalk in Toronto after the van mounted a sidewalk crashing into a number of pedestrians on Monday<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://i.dailymail.co.uk/i/newpix/2018/04/23/21/4B78638900000578-5648591-image-a-10_1524515401324.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.dailymail.co.uk%2Fi%2Fnewpix%2F2018%2F04%2F23%2F21%2F4B78638900000578-5648591-image-a-10_1524515401324.jpg&h=4cabb4eb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n Police inspect a van suspected of being involved in a collision injuring at least eight people at Yonge St. and Finch Ave<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://i.dailymail.co.uk/i/newpix/2018/04/23/19/4B78047600000578-5648591-image-m-27_1524508071559.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.dailymail.co.uk%2Fi%2Fnewpix%2F2018%2F04%2F23%2F19%2F4B78047600000578-5648591-image-m-27_1524508071559.jpg&h=9fa2db8c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n The van fled the scene after striking the pedestrians. Cops were able to stop the driver a few blocks away<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://i.dailymail.co.uk/i/newpix/2018/04/23/21/4B785C5600000578-5648591-The_driver_responsible_for_the_incident_was_arrested_a_few_block-m-7_1524514453994.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.dailymail.co.uk%2Fi%2Fnewpix%2F2018%2F04%2F23%2F21%2F4B785C5600000578-5648591-The_driver_responsible_for_the_incident_was_arrested_a_few_block-m-7_1524514453994.jpg&h=782ce02a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n The driver responsible for the incident was arrested (pictured) a few blocks away after the crash<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://i.dailymail.co.uk/i/newpix/2018/04/23/21/4B78220D00000578-5648591-image-a-6_1524514437413.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.dailymail.co.uk%2Fi%2Fnewpix%2F2018%2F04%2F23%2F21%2F4B78220D00000578-5648591-image-a-6_1524514437413.jpg&h=25fd2f57&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n The suspect has not yet been identified but has been taken into custody<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://i.dailymail.co.uk/i/newpix/2018/04/23/21/4B782CA500000578-5648591-image-m-16_1524516938929.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.dailymail.co.uk%2Fi%2Fnewpix%2F2018%2F04%2F23%2F21%2F4B782CA500000578-5648591-image-m-16_1524516938929.jpg&h=0297ef86&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n Aerial grabs show the scene in Toronto where the van struck multiple pedestrians<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://i.dailymail.co.uk/i/newpix/2018/04/23/21/4B786A6B00000578-5648591-Multiple_people_Killed_in_Toronto_after_after_a_driver_mounted_a-a-19_1524516980269.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.dailymail.co.uk%2Fi%2Fnewpix%2F2018%2F04%2F23%2F21%2F4B786A6B00000578-5648591-Multiple_people_Killed_in_Toronto_after_after_a_driver_mounted_a-a-19_1524516980269.jpg&h=d7532d14&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n Multiple people were killed after the driver mounted the sidewalk. Witnesses say they saw bodies strewn across the sidewalk"},{"pid":"2512042442c56db692b333a4c471c74c7037710f","tid":639803,"uid":130105,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-23T21:17:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://i.dailymail.co.uk/i/newpix/2018/04/23/21/4B7870FF00000578-5648591-image-a-13_1524516906947.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.dailymail.co.uk%2Fi%2Fnewpix%2F2018%2F04%2F23%2F21%2F4B7870FF00000578-5648591-image-a-13_1524516906947.jpg&h=399161f9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n A Toronto police officer responds to an incident where a van struck multiple people at a major intersection <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://i.dailymail.co.uk/i/newpix/2018/04/23/19/4B78070C00000578-5648591-image-a-23_1524507982520.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.dailymail.co.uk%2Fi%2Fnewpix%2F2018%2F04%2F23%2F19%2F4B78070C00000578-5648591-image-a-23_1524507982520.jpg&h=58dd7380&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n TV helicopter pics of the hit and run shows an entire bus load of paramedics arriving at the scene in Toronto, Canada <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://i.dailymail.co.uk/i/newpix/2018/04/23/19/4B7806EB00000578-5648591-image-a-25_1524507989467.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.dailymail.co.uk%2Fi%2Fnewpix%2F2018%2F04%2F23%2F19%2F4B7806EB00000578-5648591-image-a-25_1524507989467.jpg&h=c7212a8a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n Toronto Police are at the scene and have shut down the street as first responders treat some of the injured on the sidewalk<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://i.dailymail.co.uk/i/newpix/2018/04/23/19/4B78009300000578-5648591-image-m-5_1524507699500.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.dailymail.co.uk%2Fi%2Fnewpix%2F2018%2F04%2F23%2F19%2F4B78009300000578-5648591-image-m-5_1524507699500.jpg&h=0e1203b0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n The extent of the injuries isn&rsquo;t confirmed after the van struck up to ten people on Yonge St. near Finch Ave, Toronto<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://i.dailymail.co.uk/i/newpix/2018/04/23/19/4B78006100000578-5648591-image-m-6_1524507711185.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.dailymail.co.uk%2Fi%2Fnewpix%2F2018%2F04%2F23%2F19%2F4B78006100000578-5648591-image-m-6_1524507711185.jpg&h=6c0e9995&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n A multi-casualty incident has been declared and officials are asking people to avoid the area<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://i.dailymail.co.uk/i/newpix/2018/04/23/19/4B7806FF00000578-5648591-image-a-24_1524507985090.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.dailymail.co.uk%2Fi%2Fnewpix%2F2018%2F04%2F23%2F19%2F4B7806FF00000578-5648591-image-a-24_1524507985090.jpg&h=015520e2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n Emergency vehicles blocked off the street and officials are asking people to avoid the area<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://i.dailymail.co.uk/i/newpix/2018/04/23/19/4B781D9D00000578-5648591-The_extent_of_the_injuries_isn_t_confirmed_after_the_van_struck_-m-35_1524509863294.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.dailymail.co.uk%2Fi%2Fnewpix%2F2018%2F04%2F23%2F19%2F4B781D9D00000578-5648591-The_extent_of_the_injuries_isn_t_confirmed_after_the_van_struck_-m-35_1524509863294.jpg&h=7ca52cc9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n The extent of the injuries isn't confirmed after the van struck up to ten people on Yonge St. near Finch Ave, Toronto (pictured) <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://i.dailymail.co.uk/i/newpix/2018/04/23/21/4B787D0300000578-5648591-image-a-21_1524517165198.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.dailymail.co.uk%2Fi%2Fnewpix%2F2018%2F04%2F23%2F21%2F4B787D0300000578-5648591-image-a-21_1524517165198.jpg&h=da6fd5c4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n The rented Ryder van sits on a sidewalk about a mile from where several pedestrians were injured in northern Toronto<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://i.dailymail.co.uk/i/newpix/2018/04/23/21/4B786A9D00000578-5648591-image-a-22_1524517189987.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.dailymail.co.uk%2Fi%2Fnewpix%2F2018%2F04%2F23%2F21%2F4B786A9D00000578-5648591-image-a-22_1524517189987.jpg&h=f973a9e3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n Emergency services close Yonge Street in Toronto after the van mounted a sidewalk crashing into a crowd of pedestrians <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://i.dailymail.co.uk/i/newpix/2018/04/23/21/4B786A0B00000578-5648591-image-a-20_1524517150851.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.dailymail.co.uk%2Fi%2Fnewpix%2F2018%2F04%2F23%2F21%2F4B786A0B00000578-5648591-image-a-20_1524517150851.jpg&h=018ef7f1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n Police cover over what appears to be the body of a victim of the van crash <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://video.dailymail.co.uk/video/mol/2018/04/23/3718805629904664625/1024x576_MP4_3718805629904664625.mp4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fvideo.dailymail.co.uk%2Fvideo%2Fmol%2F2018%2F04%2F23%2F3718805629904664625%2F1024x576_MP4_3718805629904664625.mp4&d=pbWIAD41y6BH%2FlEbXVH6XTCdMQr7etzq9tFbjrA%2B72k%3D&h=0180539a\" target=\"_blank\">http://video.dailymail.co.uk/video/mol/2018/04/23/3718805629904664625/1024x576_MP4_3718805629904664625.mp4</a><br />\n White van struck several pedestrians on busy corner in Toronto<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://video.dailymail.co.uk/video/mol/2018/04/23/6494200009140684987/1024x576_MP4_6494200009140684987.mp4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fvideo.dailymail.co.uk%2Fvideo%2Fmol%2F2018%2F04%2F23%2F6494200009140684987%2F1024x576_MP4_6494200009140684987.mp4&d=pbWIAD41y6BH%2FlEbXVH6XTCdMQr7etzq9tFbjrA%2B72k%3D&h=c4551149\" target=\"_blank\">http://video.dailymail.co.uk/video/mol/2018/04/23/6494200009140684987/1024x576_MP4_6494200009140684987.mp4</a><br />\n Emergency crews attend to wounded after van strikes pedestrians<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://video.dailymail.co.uk/video/mol/2018/04/23/2893755015443365775/1024x576_MP4_2893755015443365775.mp4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fvideo.dailymail.co.uk%2Fvideo%2Fmol%2F2018%2F04%2F23%2F2893755015443365775%2F1024x576_MP4_2893755015443365775.mp4&d=pbWIAD41y6BH%2FlEbXVH6XTCdMQr7etzq9tFbjrA%2B72k%3D&h=646ba0be\" target=\"_blank\">http://video.dailymail.co.uk/video/mol/2018/04/23/2893755015443365775/1024x576_MP4_2893755015443365775.mp4</a><br />\n People tend to injured pedestrians after Toronto van attack<br />\n<br />\nsource:<a href=\"http://www.dailymail.co.uk/news/article-5648591/Van-strikes-eight-pedestrians-Toronto-flees-scene.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.dailymail.co.uk%2Fnews%2Farticle-5648591%2FVan-strikes-eight-pedestrians-Toronto-flees-scene.html&d=pbWIAD41y6BH%2FlEbXVH6XTCdMQr7etzq9tFbjrA%2B72k%3D&h=dd3367b4\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.dailymail.co.uk/news/article-5648591/Van-strikes-eight-pedestrians-Toronto-flees-scene.html</a>"},{"pid":"2d32623862f047ee5c0e2d55d95eb3b1b96717fc","tid":639803,"uid":1266,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-23T21:34:50.000Z","msg":"跟著會唔會到vancity<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8e81a5b7e81a82352491e157a5dc350c9716df97"